HEADWORD: Jiffy
<hw>Jif"fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Perh. corrupt. fr.
<ets>gliff</ets>.]</ety> <altsp>[Written also <asp>giffy</asp>.]</altsp>
<def>A moment; an instant; <as>as, I will be ready in a
<ex>jiffy</ex></as>.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark> <rj><au>J. & H.
Smith.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
